## How to navigate through the dashboard to explore the dataset: 

The second dashboard brings together the details about the actor, the director of the movie, the certificate and other parameters like Gross Amount,
IMDB Rating and Meta-score. 

Personally, sometimes, I tend to like some movies just because it is directed by one of my favorite directors and/or has one of my favorite actors in it.
On the contrary, I tend to avoid certain movies for the same reasons. Hence, this dashboard can allow the user to choose a movie based on the liking and
disliking about a certain director/ actor. 

In order to choose a movie or get information about a movie, the user can choose/ click on any of the three visualizations. Since the visualizations are 
interconnected, clicking on any on of them will enable the interactivity and help them see other information about the movie as well.

The user can click on either of the following:

1) Movies Name
2) Actor's Name
3) Directors Name

Upon clicking, useful information like meta-score, gross amount and IMDB rating will be revealed. 


